{"url": "https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/227651.Among_the_Hidden", "title": "Among the Hidden", "titleComplete": "Among the Hidden (Shadow Children, #1)", "description": "SHADOW CHILDRENLuke has never been to school. He's never had a birthday party, or gone to a friend's house for an overnight. In fact, Luke has never had a friend.Luke is one of the shadow children, a third child forbidden by the Population Police. He's lived his entire life in hiding, and now, with a new housing development replacing the woods next to his family's farm, he is no longer even allowed to go outside.Then, one day Luke sees a girl's face in the window of a house where he knows two other children already live. Finally, he's met a shadow child like himself. Jen is willing to risk everything to come out of the shadows - does Luke dare to become involved in her dangerous plan? Can he afford not to?", "imageUrl": "https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1388382796i/227651.jpg", "genres": ["Childrens", "Adventure", "Science Fiction", "Teen", "Fantasy", "School", "Young Adult", "Dystopia", "Fiction", "Middle Grade"], "asin": "1416924981", "isbn": "1416924981", "isbn13": "9781416924982", "publisher": "Aladdin Paperbacks", "series": ["Shadow Children"], "author": ["Margaret Peterson Haddix"], "publishDate": 1149145200000, "characters": ["Luke Garner", "Jen"], "ratingHistogram": [2054, 6381, 26910, 43185, 44610], "ratingsCount": 123140, "reviewsCount": 6906, "numPages": 153, "language": "English", "awards": [{"name": "Pennsylvania Young Readers' Choice Award", "awardedAt": 1009872000000, "category": "Grades 6-8", "hasWon": null}, {"name": "Vermont Golden Dome Book Award", "awardedAt": 946713600000, "category": null, "hasWon": null}, {"name": "Sunshine State Young Readers Award", "awardedAt": 978336000000, "category": "Grades 6-8", "hasWon": null}, {"name": "California Young Readers Medal", "awardedAt": 978336000000, "category": "Middle School/Juni