{"url": "https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/213753.Life_As_We_Knew_It", "title": "Life As We Knew It", "titleComplete": "Life As We Knew It (Last Survivors, #1)", "description": "Miranda\u2019s disbelief turns to fear in a split second when a meteor knocks the moon closer to the earth. How should her family prepare for the future when worldwide tsunamis wipe out the coasts, earthquakes rock the continents, and volcanic ash blocks out the sun? As summer turns to Arctic winter, Miranda, her two brothers, and their mother retreat to the unexpected safe haven of their sunroom, where they subsist on stockpiled food and limited water in the warmth of a wood-burning stove.Told in journal entries, this is the heart-pounding story of Miranda\u2019s struggle to hold on to the most important resource of all--hope--in an increasingly desperate and unfamiliar world.", "imageUrl": "https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1328012816i/213753.jpg", "genres": ["Post Apocalyptic", "Science Fiction", "Teen", "Fantasy", "Apocalyptic", "Young Adult", "Dystopia", "Fiction", "Audiobook", "Survival"], "publisher": "HMH Books for Young Readers", "series": ["Last Survivors"], "author": ["Susan Beth Pfeffer"], "publishDate": 1159686000000, "characters": ["Laura Evans", "Matt Evans", "Jonny Evans", "Miranda Evans"], "places": ["Howell, Pennsylvania", "Pennsylvania"], "ratingHistogram": [4120, 8617, 27865, 43616, 42676], "ratingsCount": 126894, "reviewsCount": 10574, "numPages": 337, "language": "English", "awards": [{"name": "Buxtehuder Bulle", "awardedAt": 1262332800000, "category": null, "hasWon": null}, {"name": "South Carolina Book Award", "awardedAt": 1230796800000, "category": "Young Adult Book", "hasWon": null}, {"name": "Rhode Island Teen Book Award", "awardedAt": 1199174400000, "category": "", "hasWon": null}, {"name": "Evergreen Teen Book Award", "awardedAt": 1230796800000, "category": null, "hasWon": null}, {"name": "The Inky Awards", "a