{"url": "https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/285205.Blood_Bound", "title": "Blood Bound", "titleComplete": "Blood Bound (Mercy Thompson, #2)", "description": "Under the rule of science, there are no witch burnings allowed, no water trials or public lynchings. In return, the average law-abiding, solid citizen has little to worry about from the things that go bump in the night. Sometimes I wish I was an average citizen...Mechanic Mercy Thompson has friends in low places-and in dark ones. And now she owes one of them a favor. Since she can shapeshift at will, she agrees to act as some extra muscle when her vampire friend Stefan goes to deliver a message to another of his kind.But this new vampire is hardly ordinary-and neither is the demon inside of him.", "imageUrl": "https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1358229157i/285205.jpg", "genres": ["Supernatural", "Shapeshifters", "Werewolves", "Fantasy", "Urban Fantasy", "Vampires", "Paranormal Romance", "Fiction", "Paranormal", "Romance"], "asin": "0441014739", "isbn": "0441014739", "isbn13": "9780441014736", "publisher": "Ace", "series": ["Mercy Thompson World", "Mercy Thompson"], "author": ["Patricia Briggs"], "publishDate": 1170144000000, "characters": ["Tony Montenegro", "Andre (The Courtier)", "Samuel Cornick", "Honey Jorgenson", "Bran \"The Marrok\" Cornick", "Ben Shaw", "Uncle Mike", "Mercy Thompson", "Gabriel Sandoval", "Zee (Siebold Adelbertsmiter)", "Wulfe", "Kyle Brooks", "Jesse Hauptman", "Darryl Zao", "Marsilia", "Adam Hauptman", "Charles Cornick", "Warren Smith", "Stefan Uccello"], "places": ["The United States of America", "Tri-Cities, Washington", "Washington (state)"], "ratingHistogram": [577, 1997, 16245, 46858, 60515], "ratingsCount": 126192, "reviewsCount": 4698, "numPages": 292, "language": "English"}
