{"url": "https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/389627.Diary_of_a_Wimpy_Kid", "title": "Diary of a Wimpy Kid", "titleComplete": "Diary of a Wimpy Kid (Diary of a Wimpy Kid, #1)", "description": "Greg Heffley finds himself thrust into a new year and a new school where undersize weaklings share the corridors with kids who are taller, meaner and already shaving.Desperate to prove his new found maturity, which only going up a grade can bring, Greg is happy to have his not-quite-so-cool sidekick, Rowley, along for the ride. But when Rowley's star starts to rise, Greg tries to use his best friend's popularity to his own advantage. Recorded in his diary with comic pictures and his very own words, this test of Greg and Rowley's friendship unfolds with hilarious results.", "imageUrl": "https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1388183826i/389627.jpg", "genres": ["Childrens", "Humor", "Graphic Novels", "Diary", "Comics", "Young Adult", "Fiction", "Middle Grade", "Realistic Fiction", "Comedy"], "asin": "0810993139", "isbn": "0810993139", "isbn13": "9780810993136", "publisher": "Amulet Books", "series": ["Diary of a Wimpy Kid"], "author": ["Jeff Kinney"], "publishDate": 1175410800000, "characters": ["Rowley", "Greg Heffley", "Manny Heffley", "Rodrick Heffley"], "ratingHistogram": [29616, 46228, 125879, 164860, 296544], "ratingsCount": 663127, "reviewsCount": 21186, "numPages": 226, "language": "English", "awards": [{"name": "Borders Original Voices Award", "awardedAt": 1167638400000, "category": "YA or Independent Reader", "hasWon": null}, {"name": "Books I Loved Best Yearly (BILBY) Awards", "awardedAt": 1262332800000, "category": "Younger Readers (2010, 2012)", "hasWon": null}, {"name": "West Australian Young Readers' Book Award (WAYRBA)", "awardedAt": 1230796800000, "category": "Younger Readers", "hasWon": null}, {"name": "Vermont Golden Dome Book Award", "awardedAt": 1230796800000, "category": null, "hasWon": null}, {"name": "North Ca