{"url": "https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/6468666-the-reckoning", "title": "The Reckoning", "titleComplete": "The Reckoning (Darkest Powers, #3)", "description": "Chloe Saunders is fifteen and would love to be normal. Unfortunately, Chloe happens to be a genetically engineered necromancer who can raise the dead without even trying. She and her equally gifted (or should that be 'cursed'?) friends are now running for their lives from the evil corporation that created them.As if that's not enough, Chloe is struggling with her feelings for Simon, a sweet-tempered sorcerer, and his brother Derek, a not so sweet-tempered werewolf. And she has a horrible feeling she's leaning towards the werewolf...Definitely not normal.", "imageUrl": "https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1327154591i/6468666.jpg", "genres": ["Magic", "Ghosts", "Supernatural", "Werewolves", "Fantasy", "Urban Fantasy", "Young Adult", "Fiction", "Paranormal", "Romance"], "asin": "1841497126", "isbn": "1841497126", "isbn13": "9781841497129", "publisher": "Orbit", "series": ["Darkest Powers"], "author": ["Kelley Armstrong"], "publishDate": 1270537200000, "characters": ["Derek Souza", "Chloe Saunders", "Victoria 'Tori' Enright", "Simon Bae"], "ratingHistogram": [1986, 4520, 19112, 35430, 54873], "ratingsCount": 115921, "reviewsCount": 3788, "numPages": 391, "language": "English", "awards": [{"name": "Teen Read Award", "awardedAt": 1262332800000, "category": "Best Read", "hasWon": null}, {"name": "Goodreads Choice Award", "awardedAt": 1262332800000, "category": "Young Adult Fantasy, for Favorite Book and for Goodreads Author", "hasWon": null}]}
