{"url": "https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/58679358-one-of-us-is-lying", "title": "One of Us Is Lying", "titleComplete": "One of Us Is Lying (One of Us is Lying, #1)", "description": "Pay close attention and you might solve this.On Monday afternoon, five students at Bayview High walk into detention. Bronwyn, the brain, is Yale-bound and never breaks a rule. Addy, the beauty, is the picture-perfect homecoming princess. Nate, the criminal, is already on probation for dealing. Cooper, the athlete, is the all-star baseball pitcher. And Simon, the outcast, is the creator of Bayview High's notorious gossip app.Only, Simon never makes it out of that classroom. Before the end of detention Simon's dead. And according to investigators, his death wasn't an accident. On Monday, he died. But on Tuesday, he'd planned to post juicy reveals about all four of his high-profile classmates, which makes all four of them suspects in his murder. Or are they the perfect patsies for a killer who's still on the loose?Everyone has secrets, right? What really matters is how far you would go to protect them.", "imageUrl": "https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1632078539i/58679358.jpg", "genres": ["Crime", "Mystery Thriller", "Murder Mystery", "Contemporary", "Young Adult", "Fiction", "Mystery", "Audiobook", "Romance", "Thriller"], "asin": "0593565371", "isbn": "0593565371", "isbn13": "9780593565377", "publisher": "Delacorte Press", "series": ["One of Us Is Lying"], "author": ["Karen M. McManus"], "publishDate": 1638259200000, "characters": ["Maeve Rojas", "Cooper Clay", "Simon Kelleher", "Nate Macaulay", "Bronwyn Rojas", "Ashton Prentiss", "TJ Forrester", "Addy Prentiss", "Jake Riordan"], "places": ["Bayview, California"], "ratingHistogram": [11960, 38532, 165505, 313215, 241077], "ratingsCount": 770289, "reviewsCount": 65334, "numPages": 416, "language": "English", "awards": [{"name": "South Carolina Book Award", "awardedAt": 1577865600000, "c