{"url": "https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/10967.The_Fiery_Cross", "title": "The Fiery Cross", "titleComplete": "The Fiery Cross (Outlander, #5)", "description": "The year is 1771, and war is coming. Jamie Fraser\u2019s wife tells him so. Little as he wishes to, he must believe it, for hers is a gift of dreadful prophecy\u2014a time-traveler\u2019s certain knowledge. Claire\u2019s unique view of the future has brought him both danger and deliverance in the past; her knowledge of the oncoming revolution is a flickering torch that may light his way through the perilous years ahead\u2014or ignite a conflagration that will leave their lives in ashes.", "imageUrl": "https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1407366842i/10967.jpg", "genres": ["Adventure", "Time Travel", "Historical Romance", "Fantasy", "Historical", "Fiction", "Audiobook", "Adult", "Historical Fiction", "Romance"], "asin": "0440221668", "isbn": "0440221668", "isbn13": "9780440221661", "publisher": "Dell", "series": ["Outlander"], "author": ["Diana Gabaldon"], "publishDate": 1125385200000, "characters": ["Brianna Randall", "Jeremiah MacKenzie", "Stephen Bonnet", "Duncan Innes", "Jocasta Cameron", "Germain Fraser", "Claire Randall Fraser", "Roger MacKenzie", "Fergus Fraser", "Young Ian Murray", "Jamie Fraser", "Marsali Fraser"], "places": ["Mount Holicon, The Royal Colony of North Carolina", "North Carolina"], "ratingHistogram": [1978, 6566, 31297, 63249, 102431], "ratingsCount": 205521, "reviewsCount": 8654, "numPages": 1443, "language": "English"}
