{"url": "https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/13831.Alanna", "title": "Alanna: The First Adventure", "titleComplete": "Alanna: The First Adventure (Song of the Lioness, #1)", "description": "From now on I'm Alan of Trebond, the younger twin. I'll be a knight.And so young Alanna of Trebond begins the journey to knighthood. Though a girl, Alanna has always craved the adventure and daring allowed only for boys; her twin brother, Thom, yearns to learn the art of magic. So one day they decide to switch places: Thom heads for the convent to learn magic; Alanna, pretending to be a boy, is on her way to the castle of King Roald to begin her training as a page.  But the road to knighthood is not an easy one. As Alanna masters the skills necessary for battle, she must also learn to control her heart and to discern her enemies from her allies.Filled with swords and sorcery, adventure and intrigue, good and evil, Alanna's first adventure begins - one that will lead to the fulfillment of her dreams and the magical destiny that will make her a legend in her land.", "imageUrl": "https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1388206270i/13831.jpg", "genres": ["Childrens", "Magic", "Adventure", "Teen", "Young Adult Fantasy", "Fantasy", "Young Adult", "Fiction", "Middle Grade", "High Fantasy"], "asin": "0689878559", "isbn": "0689878559", "isbn13": "9780689878558", "publisher": "Simon Pulse", "series": ["Tortall (Chronological Order)", "Song of the Lioness", "Tortall"], "author": ["Tamora Pierce"], "publishDate": 1104566400000, "characters": ["Duke Roger of Conte", "George Cooper", "Alanna of Trebond", "Raoul of Goldenlake", "Alex of Tirrigan", "Thom of Trebond", "Gareth of Naxen the Second (Gary)", "Jonathan of Conte", "Coram Smythesson"], "places": ["Tortall"], "ratingHistogram": [1865, 3459, 17786, 40714, 64523], "ratingsCount": 128347, "reviewsCount": 5924, "numPages": 274, "language": "English", "awards": [{"name": "Preis der Leseratten des 