{"url": "https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/60510.Poison_Study", "title": "Poison Study", "titleComplete": "Poison Study (Study, #1)", "description": "Choose: A quick death\u2026 or slow poison...About to be executed for murder, Yelena is offered an extraordinary reprieve. She'll eat the best meals, have rooms in the palace\u2014and risk assassination by anyone trying to kill the Commander of Ixia.And so Yelena chooses to become a food taster. But the chief of security, leaving nothing to chance, deliberately feeds her Butterfly's Dust\u2014and only by appearing for her daily antidote will she delay an agonizing death from the poison.As Yelena tries to escape her new dilemma, disasters keep mounting. Rebels plot to seize Ixia and Yelena develops magical powers she can't control. Her life is threatened again and choices must be made. But this time the outcomes aren't so clear...", "imageUrl": "https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1388519019i/60510.jpg", "genres": ["Magic", "Adventure", "Young Adult Fantasy", "Fantasy Romance", "High Fantasy", "Fantasy", "Young Adult", "Fiction", "Paranormal", "Romance"], "asin": "0778324338", "isbn": "0778324338", "isbn13": "9780778324331", "publisher": "Mira", "series": ["The Chronicles of Ixia", "Poison Study"], "author": ["Maria V. Snyder"], "publishDate": 1172563200000, "characters": ["Valek", "General Brazell", "Ari", "Maren", "Randall Scott", "Yelena Zaltana", "Commander Ambrose", "Janco"], "places": ["Ixia"], "ratingHistogram": [3115, 7015, 27037, 59439, 66420], "ratingsCount": 163026, "reviewsCount": 13358, "numPages": 427, "language": "English", "awards": [{"name": "Locus Award", "awardedAt": 1136102400000, "category": "Best First Novel", "hasWon": null}, {"name": "RITA Award by Romance Writers of America", "awardedAt": 1136102400000, "category": "First Book", "hasWon": null}, {"name": "Compton Crook Award", "awardedAt": 1136102400000, "category": "", "hasWon": null}]}
