{"url": "https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/13206760-scarlet", "title": "Scarlet", "titleComplete": "Scarlet (The Lunar Chronicles, #2)", "description": "Cinder is back and trying to break out of prison\u2015even though she'll be the Commonwealth's most wanted fugitive if she does\u2015in this second installment from Marissa Meyer. Halfway around the world, Scarlet Benoit's grandmother is missing. It turns out there are many things Scarlet doesn't know about her grandmother, or the grave danger she has lived in her whole life. When Scarlet encounters Wolf, a street fighter who may have information as to her grandmother's whereabouts, she is loath to trust this stranger, but is inexplicably drawn to him, and he to her. As Scarlet and Wolf unravel one mystery, they encounter another when they meet Cinder. Now, all of them must stay one step ahead of the vicious Lunar Queen Levana. The adventure continues in this fresh fairytale retelling that combines elements of Cinderella and Little Red Riding Hood.", "imageUrl": "https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1470056982i/13206760.jpg", "genres": ["Science Fiction", "Young Adult Fantasy", "Fantasy", "Young Adult", "Dystopia", "Fairy Tales", "Retellings", "Fiction", "Audiobook", "Romance"], "asin": "0312642962", "isbn": "0312642962", "isbn13": "9780312642969", "publisher": "Feiwel & Friends", "series": ["The Lunar Chronicles"], "author": ["Marissa Meyer"], "publishDate": 1360051200000, "characters": ["Scarlet Benoit", "Ran Kesley", "Aimery Park", "Linh Cinder", "Ze\u2019ev \"Wolf\" Kesley", "Carswell Thorne", "Iko", "Queen Levana", "Linh Pearl", "Michelle Benoit", "Emperor Kai", "Linh Adri"], "places": ["New Beijing, Eastern Commonwealth", "Toulouse", "Paris", "Rieux"], "ratingHistogram": [2554, 8213, 55622, 159000, 180599], "ratingsCount": 405988, "reviewsCount": 37796, "numPages": 454, "language": "English", "awards": [{"name": "Goodreads Choice Award", "awardedAt": 135702720