{"url": "https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/6442769-paper-towns", "title": "Paper Towns", "titleComplete": "Paper Towns", "description": "Who is the real Margo?Quentin Jacobsen has spent a lifetime loving the magnificently adventurous Margo Roth Spiegelman from afar. So when she cracks open a window and climbs into his life\u2014dressed like a ninja and summoning him for an ingenious campaign of revenge\u2014he follows. After their all-nighter ends, and a new day breaks, Q arrives at school to discover that Margo, always an enigma, has now become a mystery. But Q soon learns that there are clues\u2014and they're for him. Urged down a disconnected path, the closer he gets, the less Q sees the girl he thought he knew...", "imageUrl": "https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1349013610i/6442769.jpg", "genres": ["Adventure", "Teen", "Young Adult Contemporary", "Contemporary", "Young Adult", "Fiction", "Mystery", "Realistic Fiction", "Coming Of Age", "Romance"], "asin": "B003F76HBG", "isbn": "014241493X", "isbn13": "9780142414934", "publisher": "Speak", "author": ["John Green", "G\u00e1zsity Mila"], "publishDate": 1253602800000, "characters": ["Jason Worthington", "Marcus \"Radar\" Lincoln", "Lacey Pemberton", "Ben Starling", "Quentin  Jacobsen", "Margo Roth Spiegelman"], "places": ["Agloe, New York", "Orlando, Florida"], "ratingHistogram": [41185, 123480, 354835, 415813, 361939], "ratingsCount": 1297252, "reviewsCount": 55185, "numPages": 305, "language": "English", "awards": [{"name": "Anthony Award", "awardedAt": 1230796800000, "category": "Best Children's/Young Adult Novel", "hasWon": null}, {"name": "Edgar Award", "awardedAt": 1230796800000, "category": "Best Young Adult", "hasWon": null}, {"name": "Rhode Island Teen Book Award", "awardedAt": 1262332800000, "category": "", "hasWon": null}, {"name": "Deutscher Jugendliteraturpreis", "awardedAt": 1293868800000, "category": "Preis der Jugendjury", "hasWon": null}, {"name":