{"url": "https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/42900.Lover_Awakened", "title": "Lover Awakened", "titleComplete": "Lover Awakened (Black Dagger Brotherhood, #3)", "description": "In the shadows of the night in Caldwell, New York, there\u2019s a deadly war raging between vampires and their slayers. And there exists a secret band of brothers like no other - six vampire warriors, defenders of their race. Of these, Zsadist is the most terrifying member of the Black Dagger Brotherhood.A former blood slave, the vampire Zsadist still bears the scars from a past filled with suffering and humiliation. Renowned for his unquenchable fury and sinister deeds, he is a savage feared by humans and vampires alike. Anger is his only companion, and terror is his only passion\u2014until he rescues a beautiful aristocrat from the evil Lessening Society.Bella is instantly entranced by the seething power Zsadist possesses. But even as their desire for one another begins to overtake them both, Zsadist\u2019s thirst for vengeance against Bella\u2019s tormentors drives him to the brink of madness. Now, Bella must help her lover overcome the wounds of his tortured past, and find a future with her\u2026", "imageUrl": "https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1388773547i/42900.jpg", "genres": ["Supernatural", "Fantasy", "Urban Fantasy", "Vampires", "Paranormal Romance", "Adult", "Fiction", "Erotica", "Paranormal", "Romance"], "asin": "0451219368", "isbn": "0451219368", "isbn13": "9780451219367", "publisher": "Signet", "series": ["Black Dagger Brotherhood"], "author": ["J.R. Ward"], "publishDate": 1157439600000, "characters": ["John Matthew", "Mary Luce", "Rhage", "Wrath (Blind King)", "Butch O'Neal", "Zsadist", "Vishous (Black Dagger)", "Tohrment", "The Scribe Virgin", "Bella Soang", "Marissa", "Rehvenge", "Wellesandra", "Beth (Elizabeth) Randall", "Phury"], "places": ["Caldwell, New York"], "ratingHistogram": [1606, 3663, 18096, 47073, 107694], "ratin