{"url": "https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/256683.City_of_Bones", "title": "City of Bones", "titleComplete": "City of Bones (The Mortal Instruments, #1)", "description": "When fifteen-year-old Clary Fray heads out to the Pandemonium Club in New York City, she hardly expects to witness a murder\u2015 much less a murder committed by three teenagers covered with strange tattoos and brandishing bizarre weapons. Then the body disappears into thin air. It's hard to call the police when the murderers are invisible to everyone else and when there is nothing\u2015not even a smear of blood\u2015to show that a boy has died. Or was he a boy?This is Clary's first meeting with the Shadowhunters, warriors dedicated to ridding the earth of demons. It's also her first encounter with Jace, a Shadowhunter who looks a little like an angel and acts a lot like a jerk. Within twenty-four hours Clary is pulled into Jace's world with a vengeance when her mother disappears and Clary herself is attacked by a demon. But why would demons be interested in ordinary mundanes like Clary and her mother? And how did Clary suddenly get the Sight? The Shadowhunters would like to know...", "imageUrl": "https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1432730315i/256683.jpg", "genres": ["Magic", "Supernatural", "Young Adult Fantasy", "Fantasy", "Urban Fantasy", "Vampires", "Young Adult", "Fiction", "Paranormal", "Romance"], "asin": "1416914285", "isbn": "1416914285", "isbn13": "9781416914280", "publisher": "Margaret K. McElderry Books", "series": ["Shadowhunter Chronicles", "The Mortal Instruments"], "author": ["Cassandra Clare"], "publishDate": 1174978800000, "characters": ["Jonathan \"Jace\" Wayland", "Simon Lewis", "Clarissa \"Clary\" Fray", "Magnus Bane", "Jocelyn Fray", "Valentine Morgenstern", "Isabelle \"Izzy\" Sophia Lightwood", "Luke Garroway", "Alexander \"Alec\" Lightwood"], "places": ["New York City, New York"], "ratingHistogram": [54437, 107620, 345641,